data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bath city home! Located in the heart of Philadelphia, this property offers a updated, comfortable and convenient urban living experience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting living space. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a perfect space for entertaining friends and family. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, plenty of cabinet storage, and a spacious countertop, making meal preparation a breeze. Whether you're cooking a gourmet feast or enjoying a quick snack, this kitchen has you covered. The three bedrooms are well-proportioned and offer cozy retreats for rest and relaxation.  The bathroom is stylishly designed and features a bathtub/shower combination, a vanity with a sink, and a toilet. It's the perfect place to unwind after a long day or prepare for the day ahead! This home is conveniently located near various amenities such as shops, restaurants, parks, and public transportation options. Whether you need to commute to work or explore the city's vibrant offerings, everything is within easy reach. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful city home your own. Schedule a showing today and experience urban living at its finest!
